articles.description: Reggie Lynch maintains his innocence for sexual misconduct allegations but dropped appeals of his University of Minnesota expulsion because he did not feel he could receive a fair hearing.
articles.headline: Reggie Lynch drops appeals of sexual misconduct rulings, accepts expulsion

articles.description: A U.S. District Court judge denied a motion Thursday to dismiss federal criminal charges against former Adidas executives James Gatto and Merl Code and former sports agent Christian Dawkins in the FBI's investigation into college basketball corruption.
articles.headline: Judge denies motion to drop charges in corruption case against ex-Adidas execs, agent

articles.description: With Kentucky missing an edge, along with a couple of pieces, could the reeling Wildcats miss the NCAA tourney for the second time under John Calipari?
articles.headline: Is this John Calipari's most disappointing Kentucky team ever?

images.caption: John Calipari has looked for ways to reach his young Kentucky team but hasn't found one yet.
images.name: John Calipari [576x324]

articles.description: Have Oklahoma's recent troubles made Trae Young not a sure thing for the Wooden Award? Arizona's Deandre Ayton is among the players who might get another look.
articles.headline: Wooden Watch: Can someone catch Trae Young?

images.caption: Seth Greenberg explains why Collin Sexton's game will translate better in the NBA than Trae Young's.
images.name: Greenberg would take Sexton over Young for NBA

articles.description: Ayton's rare combination of productivity, NBA-ready physique and upside have him neck-and-neck with Luka Doncic as the top prospect in this year's NBA draft. What questions does Ayton need to answer?
articles.headline: Why isn't Deandre Ayton the clear favorite for the No. 1 draft pick?

images.caption: How good is Deandre Ayton's case for No. 1?
images.name: Deandre Ayton [608x342]

images.caption: Arizona freshman Deandre Ayton is a force in the paint -- and one of the best players in college basketball.
images.name: Ayton's explosiveness spicing up the Widcats

videos.description: St. John's Marvin Clark II dishes the ball to Justin Simon cutting down the lane for the contested layup and a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Simon converts tough layup for 3-point play

videos.description: Arizona State's Shannon Evans II whips a pass in to De'Quon Lake for the two-handed slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Evans' crafty pass sets up Lake dunk

videos.description: St John's Kassoum Yakwe drives down the lane and nails the layup, earning him the chance for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Yakwe sinks contested layup for 3-point chance

videos.description: Arizona State's Kodi Justice dishes a no-look pass to Romello White who finishes the contested layup.
videos.headline: Justice's no-look pass sets up 3-point play

videos.description: Arizona State's Tra Holder tries driving down the lane but is rejected by St John's Marvin Clark II.
videos.headline: Clark emphatically denies Holder

videos.description: Arizona State's Shannon Evans II shows off his range and knocks down the 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Evans buries long 3-pointer

videos.description: With time running down in the first half, St John's Shamorie Ponds drives down the lane and sinks the contested layup.
videos.headline: Ponds drills layup to earn and-1 chance

videos.description: St John's Bashir Ahmed rushes back on defense and gets the block on Arizona State's Shannon Evans II in the second half.
videos.headline: Ahmed rejects Evans with big block

videos.description: Arizona State's Vitaliy Shibel sets a pick for Shannon Evans II to set up the 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Evans uses screen to drill 3-pointer

videos.description: Arizona State's Tra Holder tries taking it to the paint but is rejected by Tariq Owens late in the second half.
videos.headline: Owens swats Holder for key block

videos.description: Arizona State's Tra Holder finds Kodi Justice in the corner for a big 3-pointer late in the game.
videos.headline: Justice knocks down clutch 3-pointer

videos.description: Arizona State's Remy Martin finds Romello White down low for the key layup to extend the Sun Devils lead.
videos.headline: White drains tough layup
